{"type":"message","id":"578ce28c","parentId":"2be45b40","timestamp":"2026-03-20T03:20:08.098Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_85v4xyeguava_1","toolName":"session_status","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 11:20 (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 6.3k in / 846 out · 💵 Cost: $0.0038\n🗄️ Cache: 97% hit · 223k cached, 102 new\n📚 Context: 41k/200k (21%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 17% left ⏱3h 39m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"}],"details":{"ok":true,"sessionKey":"agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d","changedModel":false,"statusText":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 11:20 (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 6.3k in / 846 out · 💵 Cost: $0.0038\n🗄️ Cache: 97% hit · 223k cached, 102 new\n📚 Context: 41k/200k (21%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 17% left ⏱3h 39m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773976808095}}
